<div class="container mt-4 mb-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4 fw-bold">ABCD Mall – Contact & Introduction</h1>

    <!-- Mall Introduction -->
    <div class="card shadow mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="fw-bold">About ABCD Mall</h2>
            <p class="mt-3">
                ABCD Mall, located in suburban Mumbai, is one of the region’s most iconic shopping
                and entertainment destinations. Developed by <strong>ABCD Developers Pvt Ltd</strong>,
                the mall spans over <strong>250,000 sq ft</strong> with a remarkable <strong>700 ft frontage</strong>.
                Designed by Cooper and partners, the architecture blends modern aesthetics with
                customer-centric convenience.
            </p>

            <p>
                The mall consists of four spacious and fully air-conditioned floors, each
                measuring approximately <strong>80,000 sq ft</strong>. A massive <strong>7-level parking facility</strong>
                ensures seamless accessibility for thousands of visitors daily.
            </p>

            <p>
                With a mission to enhance customer experience, the ABCD Mall website allows
                visitors to browse shop listings, explore food court menus, book movie tickets,
                view gallery images, and send valuable feedback. ABCD Mall continues to be a
                trusted place where families, shoppers, and cinema lovers gather every day.
            </p>

            <div class="text-center mt-4">
                <img src="~/Content/Uploads/Contact/mallspace.jpg"
                     class="img-fluid rounded shadow"
                     style="max-height:350px; object-fit:cover;" />


                <p class="mt-2 text-muted">A glimpse of the spacious and modern interior at ABCD Mall.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Cinema Section -->
    <div class="card shadow mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="fw-bold">Cinema & Entertainment</h2>
            <p class="mt-3">
                The ABCD Mall multiplex is one of the main attractions for movie lovers across Mumbai.
                Equipped with modern digital screening technology, surround sound, and premium seating,
                it offers a world-class entertainment experience.
            </p>

            <p>
                Through the website, customers can check available movie lists, seat availability,
                and book tickets online. When all seats are booked, the system automatically prevents
                further reservations, ensuring fair and transparent ticketing.
            </p>

            <div class="text-center mt-4">
                <img src="~/Content/Uploads/Contact/cinema2.jpg"
                     class="img-fluid rounded shadow"
                     style="max-height:350px; object-fit:cover;" />


                <p class="mt-2 text-muted">State-of-the-art multiplex cinema inside ABCD Mall.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Customer Crowd Section -->
    <div class="card shadow mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="fw-bold">Customer Trust & Popularity</h2>
            <p class="mt-3">
                Over the years, ABCD Mall has become a trusted and beloved shopping destination.
                Weekends and holidays often see thousands of enthusiastic visitors exploring shops,
                enjoying food, and spending quality time with family.
            </p>

            <p>
                The mall’s popularity is a reflection of its consistent service quality, strong brand
                presence, and commitment to customer satisfaction. Families and tourists alike choose
                ABCD Mall for memorable shopping and entertainment experiences.
            </p>

            <div class="text-center mt-4">
                <img src="~/Content/Uploads/Contact/crowdedmallcustomers.jpg"
                     class="img-fluid rounded shadow"
                     style="max-height:350px; object-fit:cover;" />


                <p class="mt-2 text-muted">Large crowds showing their trust and love for ABCD Mall.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact Information -->
    <div class="card shadow">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="fw-bold">Contact Information</h2>
            <p class="mt-3"><strong>Address:</strong> XYZ Road, Sub-urban Mumbai, India</p>
            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +91 98765 43210</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> contact@abcdmall.com</p>
            <p><strong>Opening Hours:</strong> 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM (Monday – Sunday)</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
